anywhere, Mr. Perfect.

05:35.335 --> 05:36.919
Oh, shit.

05:37.754 --> 05:41.424
Hey, man, l bet you can't hit that
light from all the way back here.

05:42.259 --> 05:44.635
What? No, we're
gonna get busted.

05:44.720 --> 05:46.554
"Steve, we're gonna
get busted."

05:50.100 --> 05:52.101
