crippling anxiety, do you?

11:17.093 --> 11:18.385
Say no.

11:20.597 --> 11:21.805
No.
No.

11:23.933 --> 11:25.726
All right, then.

11:29.689 --> 11:33.067
Go ahead in.
Show is about to start.

11:54.339 --> 11:55.839
Welcome.

11:55.924 --> 11:58.384
Welcome to the
Cirque du Freak,

11:58.468 --> 12:03.347
the oldest continuously operating
freak show in the Western hemisphere.

12:03.431 --> 12:05.265
We have toured
for 500 years,

12:05.350 --> 12:09.311
