14:23.655 --> 14:27.699
And next,
Evra the Snake Boy!

14:48.721 --> 14:49.972
Stay, Bippo.

14:50.557 --> 14:55.310
So, l'm Evra Von Britow,
and we are Serpentine.

14:55.478 --> 14:57.604
