14:57.689 --> 15:01.650
There'll be some CDs for sale in the
lobby immediately following the show.

15:09.200 --> 15:10.909
Bippo! No!

15:11.452 --> 15:13.161
Bippo, drop it,
spit that out!

15:13.246 --> 15:15.872
Yes, l'm glad you're all enjoying
this so much. lt's awesome.

15:15.957 --> 15:18.542
Evra, please
be professional.

15:18.918 --> 15:21.753
lt's not my fault.
l just want to play music.

15:21.838 --> 15:23.255
