15:23.339 --> 15:24.590
But...

15:24.674 --> 15:26.466
And now,

15:27.093 --> 15:30.345
the voluptuous,
the exotic,

15:31.472 --> 15:35.309
the insightful
Madame Truska!

15:43.818 --> 15:47.529
Do we have someone brave
enough to be my assistant?

15:47.697 --> 15:49.197
Over here.
Oh, yeah.

15:49.282 --> 15:51.116
Come on. Come on.

15:52.035 --> 15:53.035
You.

16:20.271 --> 16:22.022
Who are you?

16:23.775 --> 16:28.570
My name is Fred Smith.
l'm from out of town.

16:47.757 --> 16:50.926
Larten, finish your act quickly,
and let's leave this town early.

16:51.010 --> 16:52.803
What? l have someone
here tonight.

16:53.680 --> 16:55.180
Ready for more?

16:55.264 --> 16:58.308
Larten Crepsley
and Madam Octa!

17:00.103 --> 17:03.063
