As long as l stay calm...

18:15.887 --> 18:17.512
She's beautiful.

18:17.805 --> 18:20.849
lf l could just get
my flute, that usually...

19:01.265 --> 19:04.267
Darren. His name's
not Larten Crepsley.

19:04.352 --> 19:06.394
lt's Vur Horsten.
He's a vampire.

19:07.730 --> 19:10.315
l saw his painting
in one of my vampire books.

19:13.402 --> 19:15.821
lt's him. He's got
the same scars,

19:15.905 --> 19:18.073
the same hair,
the same everything.

19:20.201 --> 19:21.618
You seriously think
he's a vampire?

19:21.702 --> 19:22.911
Yeah.

19:40.429 --> 19:42.931
May l have my spider
back, please?

19:46.811 --> 19:49.604
Now, boys,
vampires don't exist,

19:49.689 --> 19:53.316
but if one did and he
thought someone knew,

19:53.401 --> 19:55.777
he might smother them
in their sleep.

19:57.697 --> 20:00.198
That's it! Show's over!

20:00.700 --> 20:02.826
lt's Mr. Kersey.
Come on, let's go.

20:02.910 --> 20:06.621
By order of the Health lnspector,
this theater is shut down!

20:06.706 --> 20:08.498
Good Lord, not again.

20:08.916 --> 20:12.627
Welcome to the Cirque.
What seems to be the problem?

20:12.795 --> 20:15.171
We don't want you
filthy people here.

20:15.464 --> 20:16.506
That's not the problem.

20:16.591 --> 20:21.595
The problem is you are exploiting
these poor people for profit.

20:21.679 --> 20:26.099
Thank you. Thank you so
much for looking out for us.

20:26.183 --> 20:29.895
So you gonna let us move
in with you? Give us jobs?

20:30.605 --> 20:32.188
Freak!

20:32.732 --> 20:37.110
So clumsy. l felt like a
manatee. lt felt terrible.

20:37.194 --> 20:38.278
No.

20:43.826 --> 20:45.243
Octa.

20:52.126 --> 20:53.752
Anyone here?

20:56.672 --> 20:57.672
Whoa.

21:24.700 --> 21:28.912
Hey, Octa. l'm Darren.
l'm a big fan.

21:44.720 --> 21:47.138
We can speak in private.
lt's the only...

