in 50 years.

22:19.630 --> 22:21.840
Yes. l noticed it.

22:23.009 --> 22:26.261
Look, Vincent's dead.

22:27.304 --> 22:29.639
Murdered. Sucked dry
by one of them.

22:33.728 --> 22:35.353
They're after us, man. They're
after us. They're after us!

22:35.438 --> 22:37.355
Those damn Vampaneze!
They're gonna pick us off.

22:37.440 --> 22:39.524
First Vincent,
then you, then me.

22:39.608 --> 22:41.359
Why me before you?

22:41.444 --> 22:44.696
Well, because l'm the toughest,
and they'll save me for last.

22:44.780 --> 22:46.781
Oh. Of course,
l forgot.

22:47.491 --> 22:48.825
Well, what about
the Vampire Council?

22:48.909 --> 22:50.618
