to say about Vincent.

22:50.703 --> 22:54.831
Yes. They say good riddance.
They're a bunch of wimps now, Larten.

22:54.915 --> 22:57.834
They'll do anything to avoid
a war with the Vampaneze.

22:57.918 --> 23:02.630
There are no real generals left, hombre.
You and l were the last of the Mo-Freakins!

23:02.715 --> 23:05.300
And to top it off,
Tiny's back.

23:06.719 --> 23:09.596
Mr. Tiny?
Back from the other side?

23:09.680 --> 23:13.767
Yes! Just last week he
was at the Council Library,

23:13.851 --> 23:16.061
messing with
the Book of Souls.

23:16.145 --> 23:17.812
He's trying
to destroy us all!

23:17.897 --> 23:20.982
Megalomaniac!
That man's a megalomaniac!

23:33.162 --> 23:37.165
And those murderous,
scumbag Vampaneze,

23:37.500 --> 23:40.585
they're up to something, too,
and it's all connected.

23:40.669 --> 23:42.879
lt's all connected.
l can feel it!

23:42.963 --> 23:46.341
Come with me.
We can avenge old Vincent.

23:46.425 --> 23:47.592
Kill us some Vampaneze!

23:47.676 --> 23:49.302
No. l'm sorry.

23:49.386 --> 23:51.304
