23:53.099 --> 23:54.516
l'm done fighting.

23:54.600 --> 23:58.186
l left that life for a reason.
l'm just a vaudevillian.

23:58.270 --> 24:00.480
lt's a simple life,
and l like it.

24:02.191 --> 24:03.233
Steve.

24:03.317 --> 24:07.487
l know who you are. l know
what you are, Vur Horsten.

24:09.198 --> 24:13.451
