Let him go.

24:36.475 --> 24:39.227
Now, are you
mentally unfit?

24:39.854 --> 24:42.814
Didn't you hear me
threaten you at the show?

24:42.898 --> 24:45.233
l did.
lt was awesome.

24:46.193 --> 24:51.573
You see, l want this. l want
you to make me into a vampire.

24:52.741 --> 24:55.827
l mean, vampires, they
don't take crap from anybody.

24:55.911 --> 24:57.662
