children can't become vampires.

25:05.129 --> 25:06.337
Look, look, blood.

25:07.506 --> 25:08.756
Blood.

25:09.341 --> 25:12.343
You see, Gavner,
blood.

25:15.264 --> 25:17.849
Look, if you
become a vampire,

25:17.933 --> 25:20.894
you have to leave your
friends and your family.

25:20.978 --> 25:23.771
lt's deeply depressing.
Trust me.

25:25.065 --> 25:26.858
Now get out of here.

25:31.655 --> 25:33.948
l haven't seen
my dad in years.

25:36.118 --> 25:38.328
My mom is drunk
all the time.

25:39.788 --> 25:41.789
l absolutely hate my life.

25:43.792 --> 25:47.128
l never actually said it
before, but it's the truth.

25:49.006 --> 25:52.133
This is what
l was meant for.

25:53.552 --> 25:55.428
What you're
meant for?

25:57.640 --> 26:00.016
Well, if that's the case,
let's test your blood.

26:00.142 --> 26:01.309
No. No.

26:07.358 --> 26:10.944
Who sent you here?
Your blood tastes of evil.

26:14.031 --> 26:16.157
