be a vampire.

26:17.910 --> 26:19.160
What?

26:19.245 --> 26:21.329
l have what, bad blood?

26:22.915 --> 26:25.041
l'm never gonna
forget this.

26:26.252 --> 26:28.920
One day, l promise you,
l will hunt you down.

26:29.004 --> 26:30.296
