kill you? l could do it tonight.

26:39.390 --> 26:42.767
l could knock you out and
lay you in front of a bus,

26:42.851 --> 26:44.102
and no one
would ever know!

26:44.186 --> 26:48.773
Calm down. Save that stuff for
the enemy. He's just an idiot kid,

26:48.857 --> 26:51.567
