01:15:32.820 --> 01:15:36.865
You just sedate them and feed
a little bit, and then leave.

01:15:36.949 --> 01:15:39.034
l actually developed
the method.

01:15:39.118 --> 01:15:42.829
Well, two other vampires
and l, Gavner and Vincent.

01:15:43.748 --> 01:15:46.708
We were the freaks of the vampire
world. No one understood us.

01:15:46.792 --> 01:15:48.919
And then they
started to realize

01:15:49.003 --> 01:15:51.922
that if you don't kill your prey
every time like a little piggy,

01:15:52.006 --> 01:15:56.843
