01:20:34.497 --> 01:20:37.624
Tell the little vampire
it's time to come home.

01:20:38.417 --> 01:20:42.837
lt's almost dawn. l have a spare coffin
here. l suggest you get some rest as well.

01:20:42.922 --> 01:20:45.298
