l doubt you'd be much good in a fight.

01:20:51.096 --> 01:20:52.889
Well, what if they
hurt someone?

01:20:52.973 --> 01:20:55.391
People can look
out for themselves.

01:20:55.935 --> 01:20:58.269
You've been
looking out for me.

01:20:58.687 --> 01:21:00.396
Why?

01:21:00.481 --> 01:21:03.525
Why? Because l'm
an idiot, that's why.

01:21:04.401 --> 01:21:07.153
Only an idiot would spit
in the eye of Mr. Tiny.

01:21:07.238 --> 01:21:10.698
Because he doesn't just kill
people, he brings them back, as well.

01:21:10.783 --> 01:21:14.410
And when l finally die,
l plan on staying dead.

01:21:15.788 --> 01:21:20.291
Life may be meaningless, but
death l still have hope for.

01:21:21.418 --> 01:21:23.753
Life isn't
meaningless.

01:21:23.837 --> 01:21:28.007
Tell me that after 200 years
of it, kid. Good day.

01:21:38.352 --> 01:21:39.519
You know
l never liked him.

01:21:39.603 --> 01:21:40.728
l never did,
either.

01:21:40.813 --> 01:21:42.564
l told you
when l first saw him.

01:21:42.648 --> 01:21:44.357
Should never
have let him in.

01:21:44.441 --> 01:21:45.733
We all know
it's his fault.

01:21:45.818 --> 01:21:49.153
l just can't believe he has the
nerve to walk around in here.

01:21:49.238 --> 01:21:50.905
That poor Rebecca.

01:21:55.286 --> 01:21:58.871
They took her?
Where?

01:21:59.999 --> 01:22:05.044
l don't know, but they said
to tell you to come home.

01:22:07.047 --> 01:22:11.843
Which, of course, you're not gonna
do. Wait, Darren, Darren. No, buddy.

01:22:11.927 --> 01:22:13.177
Those guys are huge, man.

01:22:20.102 --> 01:22:22.437
Hey, Mr. and Mrs. Shan.
Hey, Annie.

01:22:22.521 --> 01:22:24.564
Steve. What are
you doing here?

01:22:25.190 --> 01:22:30.069
