You guys probably really miss your son.

01:22:30.154 --> 01:22:34.657
And my mom is drunk half the time, so
she doesn't really notice l'm there.

01:22:35.534 --> 01:22:38.161
How about you
guys adopt me?

01:22:41.498 --> 01:22:42.874
No interest?

01:22:44.251 --> 01:22:46.669
