wouldn't go for it.

01:22:47.546 --> 01:22:48.546
Hmm.

01:22:49.089 --> 01:22:50.757
How disappointing.

01:22:51.550 --> 01:22:56.179
So few "people" have the
parenting instinct the way l do.

01:23:01.935 --> 01:23:03.686
Ready for the prom?

01:23:15.741 --> 01:23:19.494
