asshole thing for you to do.

01:27:52.768 --> 01:27:56.062
Make your whole family and your
secret best friend go through all that?

01:27:56.229 --> 01:27:58.773
Look, l didn't mean
to hurt anybody, okay?

01:27:58.857 --> 01:28:00.650
Who cares what
you meant to do?

01:28:00.734 --> 01:28:03.861
What you did was take my
place. That was my dream.

01:28:05.614 --> 01:28:08.032
Steve, what are
you doing with him?

01:28:08.116 --> 01:28:10.117
