here's the deal.

01:29:01.169 --> 01:29:04.422
See, the fat guy, he still wants you on
the team, and despite everything else,

01:29:04.506 --> 01:29:07.425
you are still my best friend.
So l'll tell you what,

01:29:07.509 --> 01:29:10.636
l'll make you a deal that
might just save your ass.

01:29:10.721 --> 01:29:13.139
lf you kill your family,
l'll let the freak go.

01:29:15.058 --> 01:29:17.435
Wait. My bad,
that's backwards.

01:29:17.519 --> 01:29:20.021
lf you kill the freak,
l'll let your family live.

01:29:20.105 --> 01:29:22.606
What? Let the
juicy one go?

01:29:22.899 --> 01:29:26.402
Hey, look, man, it's part of
the plan. Talk to Mr. Tiny.

01:29:28.155 --> 01:29:29.905
So what do you say?

01:29:30.115 --> 01:29:33.367
Just kill her. Oh, yeah, you
got to drink her blood, too.

01:29:33.827 --> 01:29:35.953
You can do her in
with this.

01:30:02.981 --> 01:30:04.815
MR. TlNY: Wait!

01:30:06.985 --> 01:30:09.236
Allow him in,
gentlemen.

01:30:10.489 --> 01:30:12.490
l want to see
this play out.

01:30:13.658 --> 01:30:18.120
Man, that was pathetic. You're
totally weak. You need some blood.

01:30:21.208 --> 01:30:22.583
Murlaugh.

01:30:22.667 --> 01:30:23.793
Finally.

01:30:27.672 --> 01:30:29.757
And we thought you
weren't gonna show.

01:31:25.814 --> 01:31:27.857
l hate spiders!

01:31:47.252 --> 01:31:48.586
Darren. Come here.

01:31:50.714 --> 01:31:51.881
Okay.

01:31:55.802 --> 01:31:57.428
ls that your tail?

01:31:57.512 --> 01:31:58.804
Well, yeah.

01:31:59.055 --> 01:32:01.432
l'm really sorry l got you
involved in this, okay? l...

01:32:01.516 --> 01:32:04.935
Please stop staring.
So you really need blood?

01:32:05.896 --> 01:32:07.396
Yeah.
All right.

01:32:08.732 --> 01:32:11.901
Can you just take
a little? Go ahead.

01:32:12.736 --> 01:32:14.278
l'm offering it to you.

01:32:15.947 --> 01:32:19.700
Thanks. But l just
can't lose it.

01:32:19.784 --> 01:32:20.784
What?

01:32:21.203 --> 01:32:23.621
Whatever's still
making me human.

01:32:24.289 --> 01:32:29.501
Darren, being human's not about
what you are. lt's about who you are.

01:33:13.046 --> 01:33:14.129
No.

01:34:02.470 --> 01:34:03.762
He's all yours, lad.

01:34:24.242 --> 01:34:27.077
Good.
Right in the heart.

01:34:28.913 --> 01:34:31.915
So fair and foul a day
l have not seen.

01:34:35.587 --> 01:34:38.213
My people aren't
weak like yours.

01:34:39.257 --> 01:34:41.508
