this? l can't carry the both of you.

01:40:54.006 --> 01:40:57.634
You carry Rebecca.
l can flit now.

01:40:57.719 --> 01:40:59.386
Just like a real vampire.

01:41:01.431 --> 01:41:04.307
Oh, Larten, you did it.

01:41:04.809 --> 01:41:07.060
