l'm afraid.

01:41:50.980 --> 01:41:52.731
You know, Crepsley,
it's okay.

01:41:55.651 --> 01:41:59.613
lt's weird. l spent so much time wishing
that none of this would have happened

01:41:59.697 --> 01:42:03.867
and that we never would have been
to the Cirque in the first place.

01:42:05.912 --> 01:42:09.873
But now l really can't imagine
my life happening any other way.

01:42:13.544 --> 01:42:15.045
Dawn's coming.

01:42:16.422 --> 01:42:20.091
